= System Services (`kernel/sys`)
:toc: left
:icons: font
:sectlinks:

See also: link:index.html[Kernel Index], link:syscall.html[Syscall], link:init.html[Init]

This directory groups high-level system services including kernel system info, command line parsing, ELF/dylib loading, and related runtime facilities.

== Summary

* Maintains global system state structures.
* Implements executable and dynamic library loading support.
* Provides utility services used during initialization and runtime.

== Typical Work in This Area

* Extend loader behavior and relocation support.
* Add system metadata and runtime inspection APIs.
* Improve initialization robustness and diagnostics.

